title: Galaxy Tab S8 Ultra Impressions and OnePlus' First Folding Phone!
description:
Marques and Andrew give some first impressions on the new Samsung Galaxy Tab S8 Ultra before talking about a JerryRigEverything video where Zack cracks a OnePlus 10 Pro in half. They wrap up with a discussion about YouTube subscribers and whether or not they even matter in the age of algorithms. This is a quirky one with some good insights sprinkled throughout!
